name: Kylah Williams
description: On October 30, 2009, six days shy of her second birthday, Kylah Williams was violently assaulted by her mother’s boyfriend causing irreparable brain damage. The left side of her brain was determined to be “dead,” therefore immobilizing the right side of her body. Kylah's injuries caused her to lose the ability to sit-up, walk, or talk. Read More Proceeds from the sale of Kylah's t-shirts will be donated to help support Kylah's staggering medical care.
